<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-31-0444 </DOCNO><TEXT>The author has the opinion that a number of problems still exists in environmentallaw, especially caused by deficient systematization and harmonization.The influence of administrative courts is diminishing, due to the increasinggranting of competences to the administration which cannot be checkedjudicially (Wyhl-judgment of the Federal Constitutional Court, 19/12/85).Regarding this development the constitutional requirement of entire legalprotection has to be observed.</TEXT></DOC>